## How We Work Together

I keep things straightforward. Every WordPress SEO engagement follows a clear process:

1. **Discovery call** — We discuss your site, your goals, and your current frustrations. This is free and takes 30 minutes.
2. **Technical audit** — I crawl your site, analyse your server configuration, audit your plugins and theme, and review your Google Search Console data. You receive a prioritised report with every issue ranked by impact.
3. **Implementation** — Depending on your preference, I either make the changes myself or provide detailed instructions for your developer. Most clients prefer I handle it directly.
4. **Monitoring and iteration** — SEO is not a one-off task. I track your rankings, traffic, and Core Web Vitals over time, making adjustments as Google's algorithms evolve and your site grows.

This structured approach is consistent with how I run all my [SEO consulting](/services/seo-consulting) engagements — proven, repeatable, and focused on measurable outcomes.

